DESCRIPTION: Go implementation of the ListFeatures method handling server-side streaming RPC requests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/grpc/grpc.io/blob/main/content/en/docs/languages/go/basics.md#2025-04-08_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
