TITLE: Implementing Bidirectional Streaming RPC in Python gRPC
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of RouteChat method that handles bidirectional streaming of RouteNotes. Maintains a list of previous notes and yields matching notes based on location.
SOURCE: https://github.com/grpc/grpc.io/blob/main/content/en/docs/languages/python/basics.md#2025-04-08_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
def RouteChat(self, request_iterator, context):
    prev_notes = []
    for new_note in request_iterator:
        for prev_note in prev_notes:
            if prev_note.location == new_note.location:
                yield prev_note
        prev_notes.append(new_note)
```

