TITLE: Implementing Feature Lookup in RouteGuide Service
DESCRIPTION: Implements the getFeature method that retrieves geographic feature information for a given point. It searches through a feature list and returns the corresponding feature or creates a new empty feature if none exists.
SOURCE: https://github.com/grpc/grpc.io/blob/main/content/en/docs/languages/node/basics.md#2025-04-08_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function checkFeature(point) {
  var feature;
  // Check if there is already a feature object for the given point
  for (var i = 0; i < feature_list.length; i++) {
    feature = feature_list[i];
    if (feature.location.latitude === point.latitude &&
        feature.location.longitude === point.longitude) {
      return feature;
    }
  }
  var name = '';
