TITLE: Implementing Response-Streaming RPC in Python gRPC
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of ListFeatures method that streams multiple Feature responses based on geographic boundaries. Takes a Rectangle request containing longitude and latitude bounds and yields matching features from the database.
