TITLE: Calling Client-side Streaming RPC in Go gRPC Client
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of a client-side streaming RPC call to RecordRoute. The client sends multiple Point messages and receives a single RouteSummary response. It generates random points, sends them in sequence, and then waits for the server's response.
