TITLE: Implementing Simple RPC Server Method
DESCRIPTION: Go implementation of the GetFeature method handling simple RPC requests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/grpc/grpc.io/blob/main/content/en/docs/languages/go/basics.md#2025-04-08_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
```
func (s *routeGuideServer) GetFeature(ctx context.Context, point *pb.Point) (*pb.Feature, error) {
  for _, feature := range s.savedFeatures {
    if proto.Equal(feature.Location, point) {
      return feature, nil
    }
  }
  // No feature was found, return an unnamed feature
  return &pb.Feature{Location: point}, nil
}
```

